        DH
          HaO
            address             = MN0  (Link0,  global)
        ESP
            SPI                 = SA1_SPI (SA1 protects BU message)
        BU
            sequence            = 15
            A                   = 1
            H                   = 1
            L                   = 0
            K                   = 0
            lifetime            = 105
          PadN option
            length              = 0
