        RH
            length              = 2
            type                = 2
            segments left       = 1
            address             = MN0  (Link0,  global)
        ESP
            SPI                 = SA2_SPI (SA2 protects BA message)
        BA
            status              = 0 or 1
            K                   = 0
            sequence            = 15
            lifetime            =< 105
