        IPv6 header
            source              = RUT  (Link0,  global)
            destination         = MN0X (Link0X, global)
        RH
            length              = 2
            type                = 2
            segments left       = 1
            address             = MN0  (Link0,  global)
        ESP
            SPI                 = SA2_SPI (SA2 protects BA message)
