        IPv6 header
            source              = MN0X (Link0X, global)
            destination         = RUT  (Link0,  global)
        DH
          HaO
            address             = MN0  (Link0,  global)
        ESP
            SPI                 = SA5_SPI (SA5 protects ICMPv6 header) or
